{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_06_03",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 3話 芽衣サンタのプレゼント",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月のテンペスト、クリスマスライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Moon Tempest‚ Day of Christmas Live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……\nなんとか琴乃ちゃんに見つからずにケーキ運べたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew…\nSomehow‚ we managed to deliver the cake without her noticing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、後は本番で思い切り琴乃を喜ばせてくれ\nもちろん、ファンのことも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ now let's make Kotono really happy during the live performance.\nAnd‚ of course‚ for the fans too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1813834031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん！　どっちも任せて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! I'll handle both of them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、それとね、芽衣、後で\n{user}さんも驚かせちゃうかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ and by the way‚ later…\nMei might surprise {user}-san too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺も？　どういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "それはライブが終わってからのお楽しみだよ\nじゃ、そろそろ行ってくるね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's a secret for after the live.\nWell then‚ I'm leaving now~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、琴乃にとってもファンにとっても\n最高のクリスマスライブを届けてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ make it the best Christmas live\nfor Kotono and the fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8266.666666699997,
          "startTime": 45.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんだよ！　芽衣はみんなのサンタさんなんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Absolutely! Mei is everyone's Santa Claus.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8866.666666699999,
          "startTime": 48.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmaslivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasl-stage",
      "startTime": 47.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、メリー、クリスマーース！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Merry Christmas! Everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "今日は、芽衣達がみんなのサンタになって\n最高の想い出をプレゼントするよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ Mei will be everyone's Santa\nand present the best memories!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5200.000000000003,
          "startTime": 59.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でもクリスマスっていったら\nプレゼント交換は外せないよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ but when it comes to Christmas‚\nyou can't forget about gift exchanges‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6299.999999999997,
          "startTime": 70
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12299.999999999996,
          "startTime": 76
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11966.666666699994,
          "startTime": 75.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、みんなからもプレゼント、もらおっかな\n今から、今年一番のおっきな応援、ちょうだい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ how about we get presents from everyone too?\nStarting now‚ give the biggest support of the year!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "……うん！　ありがと、みんな！\nそれじゃ、曲行くよ～！　全力でついてきてね！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah! Thanks‚ everyone!\nWell then‚ let's go with the song~! Follow me with all your might‚ okay!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7699.999999999989,
          "startTime": 85.9666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7199.999999999989,
          "startTime": 85.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（凄い一体感だ……そうか。芽衣の言葉には）\n（一つも嘘がない。だからファンの心に響くんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Such an amazing sense of unity… I see. Mei's words…）\n（They're all true. That's why it resonates with the fans' hearts.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmaslivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasl-stage",
      "startTime": 100.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmaslivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasl-stage",
      "startTime": 100.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（……おっと、そろそろサプライズのタイミングだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Oops‚ it's about time for the surprise.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6166.666666599994,
          "startTime": 107.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmaslivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasl-stage",
      "startTime": 105.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmaslivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasl-stage",
      "startTime": 109.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、誕生日おめでとー！！\nはい、琴乃ちゃん。バースデーケーキだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ happy birthday!!\nHere you go‚ Kotono-chan. It's a birthday cake!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmaslivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasl-stage",
      "startTime": 113.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣が作ったんだよー！　可愛くない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei made it! Isn't it cute?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃はもちろん、観客席もみんな笑顔だ）\n（芽衣には、きっと人を笑顔にする才能がある――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Kotono and the audience are all smiling.）\n（Mei surely has the talent to make people smileㅡㅡ）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇねぇ！　芽衣達のライブ、どうだった？\nみんな、喜んでくれたかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hey! How was Mei and the others' live performance?\nI wonder if everyone enjoyed it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.0000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。ファンにとっても、琴乃にとっても\n最高のプレゼントになったと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I think it was the best gift\nfor the fans and for Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "良かった～\nそれじゃ後は{user}さんだけだね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's great~\nNow it's just you‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_03-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "はい、芽衣サンタから、クリスマスプレゼント！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here‚ a Christmas present from Mei Santa!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
